火酒抹呢d位"},{"pid":"38657fc4a0ae9a6e150778c95fc3fd413eeae615","tid":1972640,"uid":57308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b9c433e448596dde8f1a27c5092bfadf2921e08","tid":1972640,"uid":14536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6e14caec6c2016ba12e036cc7ad86387dc5bb953","tid":1972640,"uid":57308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b25032121222b450d17a2b6c502e42a53315ac6","tid":1972640,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T16:01:23.000Z","msg":"我會用手肘位開閂水龍頭<br />\n係屋企所有燈掣開門閂門都係咁做<br />\n保持手掌位係乾淨<br />\n因為唔想隻手掌污染到常用野<br />\neg.電話,電腦,手掣,髮夾<br />\n手肘就眼不見為淨啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T16:05:25.000Z","msg":"咁你手肘咪&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我會用紙巾隔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T16:17:15.000Z","msg":"咁會用太多紙巾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n本身已經用得好多<br />\n我會定時用消毒紙巾/火酒抹呢d位"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T16:20:35.000Z","msg":"我之前都係<br />\n但係其實其他人一掂就已經污染左<br />\n所以最後都係自己用紙巾隔住就算"},{"pid":"860b2eb0712b694c9f26536350c88f2960ac7d12","tid":1972640,"uid":67089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77e67e78a3177280140ba9471a47789e403a8593","tid":1972640,"uid":57308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d546aa99e1aa3f50a652971f94bad41dedc0ac9","tid":1972640,"uid":67089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T16:06:16.000Z","msg":"我隻手成日損關唔關洗得多手事？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T16:11:45.000Z","msg":"有冇搽嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T16:26:50.000Z","msg":"冇呀，手指至手腕d皮膚顏色比較深，又甩皮。手指成日有傷口"},{"pid":"2d96288ef4bd436a7ed08949026be52dc9cd4619","tid":1972640,"uid":63449,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T16:28:24.000Z","msg":"我覺得潔癖好撚煩<br />\n我已經癖左幾年有多 諗住meet甩佢 但係都meet唔到<br />\n反而因為疫情問題 變到更加嚴重<br />\n<br />\n係屋企 廁板蓋/洗手水嚨頭 會用廁紙包住黎開/關<br />\n掂完屋企任何一樣野都會洗手<br />\n坐廳同訓床 會分開兩條褲 （姐係坐廳條褲唔會坐上床 會換第2條褲先）<br />\n因為廳d凳好污糟 我兩老出完去唔換衫就咁坐落張凳到 <br />\n我接受唔到唔到坐完又訓返上床<br />\n<br />\n係街 掂過一樣就會即時用搓手液搓手（未有疫情前 都係咁）<br />\n盡量唔會掂d野 掂完無得搓手就唔會用自己電話<br />\n用腳開門<br />\nlift制就用廁紙禁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b762eaf4e8aaa693fd0efd6b76455454ed05940","tid":1972640,"uid":162265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T16:28:31.000Z","msg":"我都喺洗手洗到手背手腕位爛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n買完啲嘢番到屋企都將全部嘢消毒一次"},{"pid":"016993bb445effdba8b39ca3e8572799001e62b5","tid":1972640,"uid":69841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T16:29:49.000Z","msg":"屋企人係污糟邋遢嗰種先慘<br />\n唔洗手掂落啱啱晾完啲衫度 gg又要洗多鑊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n掉啲未洗嘅嘢上我張床 又要洗床單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7e21e70ba4963062b8ea36a81d7c89cb3e333e0","tid":1972640,"uid":14262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T16:32:39.000Z","msg":"每次屙完屎要沖返兩個鐘涼<br />\n<br />\n有次返工唔小心急肚痛，屙完好唔舒服。"},{"pid":"2f62a54cc8254bd7d984af9afa4413b951c4ebec","tid":1972640,"uid":36857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T16:33:26.000Z","msg":"以前細個無潔癖，成日坐地下玩唔覺得有問題<br />\n<br />\n越大個潔癖越嚴重，沖完涼之後會用消毒濕紙巾抹手機、電腦枱等，無抹過既野一律唔會掂，唔小心掂完要即刻洗手洗腳"},{"pid":"a6d8b4f3410ce984283ff13e8ab367900ea77d54","tid":1972640,"uid":126797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T16:40:21.000Z","msg":"一個住好好多，<br />\n分開邊度係乾淨，邊度係污糟，就冇咁嚴重，覺得咩都係污糟唔掂得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9fd4cb39caeb4c4336b8ba2bfa66b30a19c24f3","tid":1972640,"uid":57308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"q